Title : Faculty of Architecture, Urban Design and Creative Arts, Mahasarakham University
Text : The '''Faculty of Architecture, Urban Design and Creative Arts''' at the [[Mahasarakham University]] is hosted in [[Mahasarakham University#Khamriang Campus|Khamriang Campus]] located in the city of [[Mueang Maha Sarakham District|Mahasarakham]], [[Thailand]].

The Faculty has missions in educational development, and research, with emphasis on the integrated approach to planning, design, and [[architecture]] that will be necessary to take on the 21st century global challenges of [[urbanization]], [[environmental conservation]], and climate change, as well as preservation of arts and culture, and improved local and social development.<ref name="About Us">{{cite web
 |url=http://www.arch.msu.ac.th/en/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=78&Itemid=53 
 |title=About Us 
 |publisher=Faculty of Architecture, Urban Design & Creative Arts, MSU
 |accessdate=2014-05-03 
}}</ref><ref name="MSU Arch">{{cite web
 |url=http://www.arch.msu.ac.th/en/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=78&Itemid=53 
 |title=Faculty of Architecture, Urban Design & Creative Arts 
 |publisher=Mahasarakham University
